Install nodejs
cmd:
npm install -g json-server

Create a json file in notepad
{
  "example":
  [
    {
      "key": "value"
    }
  ]
}

In cmd
cd File Directory
json-server --watch filename.json

Go to Postman
Go to + sign 
GET method and copy paste the link
POST method body > raw > json
{
      "key": "value"
}
PATCH method: one one key is updated (specify ID)
PUT method: the whole file will be updated (specify ID)
DELETE method
